        "synopsis": {
            "value": "When a smart, handsome, and foul-mouthed doctor ‘Paniti,’ or Dr. Pup, met a hot, sexy superstar 'Kluay' they agree they are not each other's types. They hated each other at first sight, but when they have to live together, something strange happens; it looks like Dr. Pup is falling in love with Kluay. To save face from what he said before, that she is not his type, he is trying to act\n\nlike he doesn't like her, but can he?\n\nWhat will the ending of this two be, haters or lovers?\n\nEdit Translation\n\nEnglish\n\nРусский\n\nmagyar / magyar nyelv\n\ndansk",
